msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-enter-fullscreen-mode.rst:54
#: f0781550a727460b98826cdc487cc861
msgid ""
"As an alternative to the Xfce4 method, you can enable fullscreen mode for"
" selected qubes by using the `gui-allow-fullscreen <https://dev.qubes-"
"os.org/projects/core-admin-client/en/latest/manpages/qvm-features.html"
"#gui-gui-default>`__ feature of a qube."
msgstr ""

